{"tid":1318152,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"我係香焦糖 夠薑入黎隻揪啦 垃圾連登仔","createTime":"2019-07-15T01:24:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-15T09:07:29.000Z","uid":163960,"like":14,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1f28469db457e0a9530327079c7d9a7af91571fd","tid":1318152,"uid":163960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T01:24:08.000Z","msg":"對唔住呃大家入黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇完呢個facebook post<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/HK.North/permalink/1488443594629493?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2FHK.North%2Fpermalink%2F1488443594629493%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=MD3su0BfWHBnm8Iidd6ZKf2x0mEA6i1FZlyL0j1bjmE%3D&h=b6dace45\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/HK.North/permalink/1488443594629493?sfns=mo</a><br />\n我開始有個大膽既想法<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔知咁多位連登仔知唔知呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我發夢既時候知道，其實住文中地方既住戶，平時係佐敦谷公園既一啲小朋友嬉鬧聲、或者有團體係公園裡面搞活動用大聲公講野既時候，住三十幾樓既住戶依然係聽得好清楚</span></span><br />\n<br />\n咁大家都知，sing hallelujah to the lord 係強大既驅魔神器，無咩事都唔可以亂用<br />\n大家就千其唔好學屯門大媽咁唱歌，影響附近居民、製造噪音啦<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n講多一次，我呼籲大家，千其唔好係佐敦谷公園唱聖詩報佳音，影響到偉大既警務人員休息<br />\n</span></span><br />\n佢地出盡全力為香港政府服務，甚至係犧牲埋佢地偉大既肉體<br />\n所以我地要保持一個寧靜既環境，唔可以阻礙佢地係屋企休息！！！！！"},{"pid":"ffd5e2453a05364671ef6e295daa0e0ebf7a51a7","tid":1318152,"uid":153722,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T01:26:50.000Z","msg":"唱聖詩咁溫和咁好聽 可以洗滌到暴戾既心靈<br />\n<br />\n點可以話影響警務人員休息<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8348a01cb3509c19a548b7cd0dd3ae93d0cb49f0","tid":1318152,"uid":163960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ffd5e2453a05364671ef6e295daa0e0ebf7a51a7","tid":1318152,"uid